.SH "BUGS"
.PP
\fBKNOWN BUGS\fR
.IP
\fBpi\-getrom\fR does not work with OS5 devices as yet, due to changes in
the architecture and design of the Palm HotSync protocol and file type
changes from m68k to ARM. Other than that, \fBpi\-getrom\fR has no known
bugs at this time.

.PP
